song.title: Hey I Like You (Final)
song.info:
Released in the 32k Executable Music Competition at TRSAC 2015 in Aarhus, Denmark - 2nd Place
4 minutes | 14 instruments | 2.6 kilobytes
This is the final version of the track (released 2 days after the party) which features an enhanced ending and several fixes to reduce precalc time of the executable file.
